          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "I. The example for us. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "I. The example for us.",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "p",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " ",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "{1} Of how all natural and human ties and affections are to be subordinated to doing God’s will.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " Obedience to Him is the first and main thing to which everything else bows, and which determines everything.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " If others compete or interfere, reject them.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " Out of that common obedience new ties are formed among men.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " {2} Of how all these ties may be doubled in power and preciousness by being based on that obedience.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "II. The promise for us. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "II. The promise for us.",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "p",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " ",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Of Christ’s loving relationship in which He finds delight; in which He sustains and transcends all these in His own proper person and to each.",
        "children": []
      },
